{
  "stem": "23131.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So when Tovia wasn't there-- wasn't home, and I was away too, they came to my house and they took, and they looked.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they looked for me, and they looked for him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Thank God I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he wasn't secure there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He knew that, if not them, some other-- some-- somebody else will kill him there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Or they'll send him away to Russia, or something will happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He wanted to escape.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He had enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after a good year and a half, maybe two-- what year?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went in '44.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In '45, we left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we came to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Warsaw was still burning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Warsaw wasn't liberated yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was liberated, but not officially.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Warsaw was still burning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One piece of fire.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Tovia, he just closed the door and we took just what we could carry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- I was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said to his brothers, he wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's my-- my plan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You want to go, you're welcome.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Your-- my opinion is that you have to leave here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because one brother, Asael, was killed after the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was mobilized to the army, to the Russians, and he was killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The day when he was killed, his daughter, Asaela, was born in Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went first to Vilna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Vilna, he had two very good connections, my husband, with a Polish guy that was in the woods.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he hel-- and he was a big shot in Vilna, so he gave him a tremendous hand.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he sent him away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He didn't let him stay there more than a week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think Tovia met somebody in the street, and he didn't like his approach.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
